<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span> وَجْهَانِ<span class="c1">", انْتَهَى.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></span></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>"قُلْت": الصَّوَابُ عَدَمُ انْعِقَادِ الْيَمِينِ مع الإطلاق.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
